 Middle Ages <i>Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]},{"name":"De","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Hugh De Treverbyn was born in 1257, in England, United Kingdom. He married Mrs- Hugh de Trebverin about 1282, in England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1257–":"1257–Surnud","1261–Female":"1261–Surnud","1293–1349":"1293–1349","1257–Male":"1257–Surnud","1349":"1349","Abt 1282":"umbes 1282","1257":"1257","1261":"1261","1293":"1293","Of,,, England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1257–":"1257–Kuollut","1261–Female":"1261–Kuollut","1293–1349":"1293–1349","1257–Male":"1257–Kuollut","1349":"1349","Abt 1282":"noin 1282","1257":"1257","1261":"1261","1293":"1293","Of,,, England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1257–":"1257–Décédé","1261–Female":"1261–Décédée","1293–1349":"1293–1349","1257–Male":"1257–Décédé","1349":"1349","Abt 1282":"environ 1282","1257":"1257","1261":"1261","1293":"1293","Of,,, England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Hugh De Treverbyn est né en 1257, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Mrs- Hugh de Trebverin environ 1282, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1257–":"1257–Verstorben","1261–Female":"1261–Verstorben","1293–1349":"1293–1349","1257–Male":"1257–Verstorben","1349":"1349","Abt 1282":"um 1282","1257":"1257","1261":"1261","1293":"1293","Of,,, England":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Hugh De Treverbyn wurde 1257 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hat um 1282 in England, United Kingdom Mrs- Hugh de Trebverin geheiratet."},"ht":{"1257–":"1257–Desede","1261–Female":"1261–Desede","1293–1349":"1293–1349","1257–Male":"1257–Desede","1349":"1349","Abt 1282":"about 1282","1257":"1257","1261":"1261","1293":"1293","Of,,, England":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1257–":"1257–elhunyt","1261–Female":"1261–elhunyt","1293–1349":"1293–1349","125